HEADWORD: Viminal
<hw>Vim"i*nal</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>viminalis</ets> pertaining to osiers, fr. <ets>vimen</ets> a pliant
twig, osier.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to twigs; consisting of twigs;
